OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGovernment says video game 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Floot boxes will not be     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fregulated                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The UK government has decided video    
OL,6, game loot boxes will not be regulated  
OL,7, under betting laws, despite it finding 
OL,8, a link between them and gambling harms.
OL,10,FIn a long-awaited call for evidence, it
OL,11,Finstead told the video game industry to
OL,12,Ftake action to protect young people.   
OL,14,FIt says it will step in if firms do not
OL,15,Fact, and also wants loot box purchases 
OL,16,Fto be restricted to adults, unless     
OL,17,Fapproved by a parent or guardian.      
OL,19,FOne academic said he was "dismayed" by 
OL,20,Fthe government's approach.             
